  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With one of the iconic horror games of 2015 making a comeback! Fully enhanced graphics in the enhanced edition of Sad Satan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/d16fcc2ed39be9ec526602dec2eab5ff.poster.avif?t=1767887290\" width=410 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/d16fcc2ed39be9ec526602dec2eab5ff.webm?t=1767887290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/d16fcc2ed39be9ec526602dec2eab5ff.mp4?t=1767887290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Description</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sad Satan is a horror and mystery game that takes you on a terrifying journey through dark corridors and locations filled with secrets. Get ready for an experience full of puzzles and scary visuals based on real events. In this game, you will face psychological challenges and horrific scenes that will test your courage. Can you decipher the mystery and escape the nightmare? Join us now and discover the dark secrets that await you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game  you must collect all 8 books</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/8d8a43075a93d780529b6b0bdbc09345.poster.avif?t=1767887290\" width=394 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/8d8a43075a93d780529b6b0bdbc09345.webm?t=1767887290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/8d8a43075a93d780529b6b0bdbc09345.mp4?t=1767887290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Creepy atmosphere and eerie music.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Complex puzzles to solve. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Visuals and scenes based on real events. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Unique and impactful psychological experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Prepare to dive into a world of horror and face the satans within you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/09ed798ed29f086503acb56277cb2bef.poster.avif?t=1767887290\" width=410 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/09ed798ed29f086503acb56277cb2bef.webm?t=1767887290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/09ed798ed29f086503acb56277cb2bef.mp4?t=1767887290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With one of the iconic horror games of 2015 making a comeback! Fully enhanced graphics in the enhanced edition of Sad Satan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/d16fcc2ed39be9ec526602dec2eab5ff.poster.avif?t=1767887290\" width=410 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/d16fcc2ed39be9ec526602dec2eab5ff.webm?t=1767887290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/d16fcc2ed39be9ec526602dec2eab5ff.mp4?t=1767887290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Description</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sad Satan is a horror and mystery game that takes you on a terrifying journey through dark corridors and locations filled with secrets. Get ready for an experience full of puzzles and scary visuals based on real events. In this game, you will face psychological challenges and horrific scenes that will test your courage. Can you decipher the mystery and escape the nightmare? Join us now and discover the dark secrets that await you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game  you must collect all 8 books</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/8d8a43075a93d780529b6b0bdbc09345.poster.avif?t=1767887290\" width=394 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/8d8a43075a93d780529b6b0bdbc09345.webm?t=1767887290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/8d8a43075a93d780529b6b0bdbc09345.mp4?t=1767887290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Creepy atmosphere and eerie music.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Complex puzzles to solve. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Visuals and scenes based on real events. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Unique and impactful psychological experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Prepare to dive into a world of horror and face the satans within you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/09ed798ed29f086503acb56277cb2bef.poster.avif?t=1767887290\" width=410 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/09ed798ed29f086503acb56277cb2bef.webm?t=1767887290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686080/extras/09ed798ed29f086503acb56277cb2bef.mp4?t=1767887290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
